ote-at-phillips-exeter-academy-in-new-hampshire-full-text/|title=Andrew Yang Keynote at Phillips Exeter Academy in New Hampshire (Full Text)|date=2019-02-08|website=Andrew Yang for President|language=en-US|access-date=2019-04-12}}</ref> journalist [[Drew Pearson (journalist)|Drew Pearson]],<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://library.syr.edu/digital/guides/p/pearson_d.htm|title=Drew Pearson Papers An inventory of his papers at Syracuse University|website=library.syr.edu|language=en|access-date=April 7, 2018}}</ref> [[Dwight Macdonald]],<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://observer.com/2006/03/from-trotsky-to-midcult-in-search-of-dwight-macdonald/|title=From Trotsky to Midcult: In Search of Dwight Macdonald|date=March 27, 2006|work=Observer|access-date=April 7, 2018|language=en-US}}</ref> [[James F. Hoge, Jr.]],<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.imdb.com/name/nm1965959/bio|title=Jim Hoge|website=IMDb|access-date=April 7, 2018}}</ref> [[Paul Klebnikov]],<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/news/2004/jul/16/guardianobituaries.pressandpublishing|title=Obituary: Paul Klebnikov|last=Wheeler|first=Carolynne|last2=Reed|first2=Christopher|date=July 15, 2004|website=the Guardian|language=en|access-date=April 7, 2018}}</ref> [[Trish Regan]],<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.seacoastonline.com/article/20090411/news/904110324|title=PEA hosts graduate and CNBC's Trish Regan|last=Johnson|first=Tara|work=seacoastonline.com|access-date=April 7, 2018|language=en}}</ref> [[Suzy Welch]],<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://people.com/archive/new-wife-new-life-vol-63-no-15/|title=New Wife, New Life|work=PEOPLE.com|access-date=April 7, 2018|language=en}}</ref> and [[Sarah Lyall]];<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=6_RAAoUrZx8C&pg=PA291|title=The Anglo Files: A Field Guide to the British|last=Lyall|first=Sarah|date=2009|publisher=W. W. Norton & Company|isbn=978-0-393-33476-0|page=291}}</ref> actors [[Michael Cerveris]],<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.masterworksbroadway.com/artist/michael-